>

    <SlotHero>
      <Fragment slot="smltitle">
        Gold Coast Ad Videography
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Video Ad Filming and Production.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        Fully inclusive services with all labour, cameras, lenses and gimbals included in cost. With a fine eye for detail, we write and direct short form video ads and longer video for wider use. Promoting brands and products in the best light, appealing to your target market and winning over more customers. Gold Coast videography and production experts, offering a refreshing take on graphic design services.
      </Fragment>
      
    </SlotHero>

          <SectionHeadImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              Short form video ad design
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              Crafting Compelling Video Ads.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">
              My Video Ad Production services are all about crafting compelling narratives that captivate your audience's attention. I blend creativity with data-driven insights to create video ads that deliver results. From concept to execution, I've got you covered.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                src="/works/video-cameraclose.webp"
              />
            </Fragment>
          </SectionHeadImg>

          <SectionHeadSecImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              Professionally designed and scripted video ads
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              The Art of Storytelling.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">
              I understand that an effective video ad isn't just about visuals; it's about emotion, connection, and engagement. Whether it's a short, snappy social media ad or a longer-form promotional video, I'll harness the art of storytelling to make your brand message unforgettable.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                src="/works/video-filmerdark.webp"
                
              />
            </Fragment>
          </SectionHeadSecImg>

          <SectionHeadImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              Sell your product using Reels and Youtube
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              Tailored Video Ads for Your Brand.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">
              I work closely with you to understand your goals and vision. From there, I'll develop a video strategy that aligns with your brand identity, delivering video ads that resonate with your target audience and achieve your marketing objectives.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                src="/works/video-musicians.webp"
                
              />
            </Fragment>
          </SectionHeadImg>

  <Cta />

</Layout>
